list.abstract: partnership的意思是伙伴关系，合伙（关系），合伙企业。合伙企业，是指自然人、法人和其他组织依照《中华人民共和国合伙企业法》在中国境内设立的，由两个或两个以上的合伙人订立合伙协议，为经营共同事业，共同出资、合伙经营、共享收益、共担风险的营利性组织。其包括普通合伙企业和有限合伙企业。

yingyinNormal.en: Are taking the managing partnership? Where'd you hear that? Is it true?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要做管理合伙人了吗？你从哪里听来的？是不是真的？

yingyinNormal.en: Besides, he talks of the partnership between the farmers and the family, and I like that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 此外，他还提到了我们家族和佃户之间的合作关系，我挺喜欢这想法。

yingyinNormal.en: That offends you the most? Really? Not the fact that every fourth-year was promised a partnership?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那让你最生气？真的吗？而不是每个四年律师都被许诺成为合伙人吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You finally have a chance to get out from under him, take it. Managing partnership is not under him. It is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你终于有个机会与威尔平起平坐，别错过。管理合伙人就不算是他的下属了。一样是。

yingyinNormal.en: But just outside St Albans, farmer Howard Roberts is a part of one such rare partnership that survives to this day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在圣奥尔本斯 农民霍华德 罗伯特就是今天幸存的这种罕见关系的一部分。

yingyinNormal.en: If we form such a partnership, our patients would have access to more modern equipment, to more advanced treatments.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我们达成这样的合作关系，我们的病患就能用上更现代化的设备，能接受更先进的治疗。

yingyinNormal.en: This is not a partnership of equals. Nothing close to it. If you are to be my Vice President, you will do what I ask.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种合作关系并不平等，完全不平等。你要是想当我的副总统，就按我说的做。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, you're all valued employees. But as we undergo this transition to LIFE online we wanted to be candid with you that some of you will be determined non-vital employees to the new partnership.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，你们都是很有能力的员工。但是，当我们在将周刊网路化的过渡期间，我们要向你们坦白的说。
